<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tension-n">tension <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'tenʃn/    美 /'tenʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1u">1.<strong>[U] 拉伸；张力；绷紧程度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sudden tension on the line told me (that) I had hooked a fish.
线突然绷紧，说明我钓到鱼了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] (情绪上) 紧张；烦躁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Relax yourself. <strong>Ease tension</strong> by doing exercise.
放松!做做运动来放松紧张的神经。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c-u">3.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] (局势、关系或状况) 紧张：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>international tension
国际紧张局势</p></div></div>